 d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529696\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 28, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lrj1665702774450.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lrj1665702774450.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lrj1665702774450.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lrj1665702774450\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n Uniface <span class=\"ph\">10.4</span>.01: Currency Updates Since 10.3.02\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface <span class=\"ph\">10.4</span>.01 consolidates updates to platforms and connectors made in patches since 10.3.02. Documentation was updated for the following items.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__section_d401e1_d402e1_d403e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729658e55\">New LDAP U3.0\n            connector supports connections using TCP or TLS</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1304e1_d1305e1_d1306e1\">The new LDAP connector enhances security by supporting\n               TLS connections to the LDAP server. It ensures that you can comply with a recent\n               Microsoft Security Update (see <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4520412/2020-ldap-channel-binding-and-ldap-signing-requirements-for-windows\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">2020 LDAP channel binding and LDAP signing\n                  requirements for Windows</a>).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1307e1_d1308e1_d1309e1\">For more information, see <span class=\"ph\"><a class=\"xref dropDown\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mcs1665702735695.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mcs1665702735695.html\" title=\"The Uniface LDAP connector enables you to connect with LDAP servers, including stand-alone LDAP servers and X.500 Directory System Agents with an LDAP gateway installed.\">LDAP Connector</a> and <a class=\"xref dropDown\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pqn1665702774521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pqn1665702774521.html\">LDAP over TLS</a>.</span></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__section_d404e1_d405e1_d406e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729658e86\">\n            New MQL connector to support MySQL 8 on Windows\n </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1310e1_d1311e1_d1312e1\">Version 5.0 of the MQL connector is now available. To\n               use this connector, you need to copy <span class=\"ph filepath\">libmysql.dll</span> from connector\n               folder of the MySQL installation to the <span class=\"ph filepath\">common/bin</span> folder of the\n               Uniface installation.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__note_w1474ab1b5b3b3b3_w1475ab1b5b3b3_w1476ab1b5b3_w1477ab1b5_w1478ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Be sure to copy the correct version. The 32-bit and 64-bit versions are not binary compatible.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1313e1_d1314e1_d1315e1\">For more information, see <span class=\"ph\"><a class=\"xref dropDown\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bhn1665702735843.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bhn1665702735843.html\" title=\"The MySQL DBMS connector enables you to integrate MySQL databases with Uniface.\">MySQL</a>.</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__section_d407e1_d408e1_d409e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729658e119\">\n            New DBMS connector to support PostgreSQL version 12\n </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1316e1_d1317e1_d1318e1\">To use the new connector, specify PGS U1.4 in your\n               assignment file. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[DRIVER_SETTINGS]\nPGS U1.4\nUSYS$PGS_PARAMS identifiers = quoted</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1319e1_d1320e1_d1321e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref dropDown\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cgu1665702774669.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cgu1665702774669.html\" title=\"The PGS connector makes use of ODBC to connect to PostgreSQL database. You must therefore install the PostgreSQL ODBC driver before connecting Uniface to your PostgreSQL database.\">Installation and Configuration of PGS Connector</a>. </p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__section_d410e1_d411e1_d412e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729658e144\">\n            Feature: PGS\n            connector now supports the option <code class=\"ph codeph\">map fixed length to variable</code>\n               (<code class=\"ph codeph\">fv</code>) </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1322e1_d1323e1_d1324e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref dropDown\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hoa1665702732769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hoa1665702732769.html\" title=\"Map fields with a fixed length storage format (CHAR) to a variable length storage format.\">map fixed length to variable</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__section_d413e1_d414e1_d415e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729658e166\">\n            Updated Hardware\n            requirements </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1325e1_d1326e1_d1327e1\">With the updated version of Chromium Embedded Framework\n            (CEF3), the hardware requirements for the Uniface IDE and Uniface applications that run\n            HTML widgets have increased. For more information, see <a class=\"xref dropDown\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bqt1690197038987.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bqt1690197038987.html\" title=\"Uniface supports many different platforms and databases, but not all products and functionality are available on each platform.\">System Requirements for Microsoft Windows</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__section_d416e1_d417e1_d418e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729658e183\">\n            Removal of Dojo Widgets for DSPs\n </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1328e1_d1329e1_d1330e1\">The Dojo widget library will no longer be delivered in\n               future Uniface 10 installations.</p>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__note_w1479ab1b5c11b3b3_w1480ab1b5c11b3_w1481ab1b5c11_w1482ab1b5_w1483ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span>  Note: If you are still using the Dojo widgets (which were the\n               default before Uniface 9.7), we strongly urge you to switch to the normal HTML5\n               widgets. The Dojo widget library is outdated, and support for Dojo is being phased\n               out.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrj1665702774450__p_d1331e1_d1332e1_d1333e1\">The Dojo widgets files are still provided in the\n               Uniface 10.3.02 installation, but in this patch, the widget definitions are no longer\n               be provided in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">uweb.def</span> file. If you still want to use the\n               Dojo widgets: before applying this patch, copy the Dojo widget definitions from\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">uweb.def</span> to a file called <span class=\"ph filepath\">web.ini</span> in\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">uniface/adm</span> directory.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529696\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529696\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface 10.4.01: Currency Updates Since 10.3.02 Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 28, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface 10.4 .01: Currency Updates Since 10.3.02 Uniface 10.4 .01 consolidates updates to platforms and connectors made in patches since 10.3.02. Documentation was updated for the following items. New LDAP U3.0 connector supports connections using TCP or TLS The new LDAP connector enhances security by supporting TLS connections to the LDAP server. It ensures that you can comply with a recent Microsoft Security Update (see 2020 LDAP channel binding and LDAP signing requirements for Windows ). For more information, see LDAP Connector and LDAP over TLS . New MQL connector to support MySQL 8 on Windows Version 5.0 of the MQL connector is now available. To use this connector, you need to copy libmysql.dll from connector folder of the MySQL installation to the common/bin folder of the Uniface installation. Note: Be sure to copy the correct version. The 32-bit and 64-bit versions are not binary compatible. For more information, see MySQL . New DBMS connector to support PostgreSQL version 12 To use the new connector, specify PGS U1.4 in your assignment file. For example: [DRIVER_SETTINGS] PGS U1.4 USYS$PGS_PARAMS identifiers = quoted Copy For more information, see Installation and Configuration of PGS Connector . Feature: PGS connector now supports the option map fixed length to variable ( fv ) For more information, see map fixed length to variable . Updated Hardware requirements With the updated version of Chromium Embedded Framework (CEF3), the hardware requirements for the Uniface IDE and Uniface applications that run HTML widgets have increased. For more information, see System Requirements for Microsoft Windows . Removal of Dojo Widgets for DSPs The Dojo widget library will no longer be delivered in future Uniface 10 installations. Important: Note: If you are still using the Dojo widgets (which were the default before Uniface 9.7), we strongly urge you to switch to the normal HTML5 widgets. The Dojo widget library is outdated, and support for Dojo is being phased out. The Dojo widgets files are still provided in the Uniface 10.3.02 installation, but in this patch, the widget definitions are no longer be provided in the uweb.def file. If you still want to use the Dojo widgets: before applying this patch, copy the Dojo widget definitions from uweb.def to a file called web.ini in uniface/adm directory. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}